king feels more comfortable on f2.}) (8... d5 9. exd5 Ne7 $2 {doesn't make
sense, in view of} (9... Qf5 {could be tried still, though after} 10. dxc6 Qxf4
11. Qe2+ Be6 12. g3 $1 {followed by 13.cxb7 should be better for White.} (12.
cxb7 $4 {allows} Ng4+ $1 13. Kg1 Bc5+ 14. Nxc5 Qd4+)) 10. c4 $16 {[%csl Rb4]
[%cal Ya2a3]}) 9. Bd3 $1 {[%csl Gd3,Rg6]} ({An important novelty. It's
tempting chasing away the bishop with} 9. a3 $2 {but that's actually only
