(15... Bb4 16. Bd2 {Kapnisis-Katopodis, Anogia 2018} Nxd5 17. Nxd5 Bxd2+ 18.
Kxd2 cxd5 19. Rhc1 $14) 16. Bd2 (16. Ne2 $5 {perhaps keeps more life in the
position.}) 16... Ba3 17. Rd1 O-O 18. O-O Rfd8 {and White didn't have much in
